Preheat oven to 350 degrees F. Place bread cubes in single layer on baking sheet. Bake 15 minutes, or until toasted. Combine kidney beans, mozzarella, bell pepper and onions in a large bowl. Combine marinade ingredients in a medium bowl. Pour over bean mixture; toss to mix well. Add bread to bean mixture; toss to mix well. Let mixture stand 30 minutes to 1 hour, stirring occasionally. Serve over field greens.